moji\" /></blockquote><br />\n虐待動物就唔會上嚟問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T16:45:10.000Z","msg":"幫佢戴頭罩先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咬到成身傷帶出街隨時被人誤會你虐待動物"},{"pid":"2a5a0120d7afcaa650537308067b85043f37545c","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":4,"dislike":31,"score":-27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T16:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪少左陪佢，屋企死日冇人，分離焦慮？</blockquote><br />\n其實返工返學 好難全程成日都陪佢 但返到屋企點都會同佢玩 週末仲帶佢出去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee7a67c377d3fb56fa7f8efbdc54e54bd998dfd","tid":747830,"uid":148146,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T16:47:30.000Z","msg":"狗狗有冇落街嘅習慣 會唔會係惹到一啲皮下嘅寄生蟲 或者皮膚病 肉眼睇唔到但係佢又好痕所以咪不停咬嗰啲位?<br />\n又或者真係情緒有問題 好似有啲狗狗會lam自己隻手嚟解悶同發洩 佢就咬自己啲毛?<br />\n雖然我都有養狗但係真係冇見過咁嘅情況 純粹係推測一下 希望幫到你"},{"pid":"7146f5490fb313aebd2d069a17bbda26a3e7d12d","tid":747830,"uid":179990,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T16:48:07.000Z","msg":"明顯係皮膚出問題搞到佢好痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以先會咬自己止痕"},{"pid":"587cfbb73c0f0196e0af4d22eca269b42ee7ba80","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T16:50:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪敏感？</blockquote><br />\n有其中一個醫生話係 比咗啲藥 同特別嘅狗糧 但情況不單冇好轉 呢兩日仲要唔食野 真係好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00424354b4fa48a19c7d7c186f67353b0059eec9","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":5,"dislike":13,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T16:51:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾主人<br />\n講完[img]assets/faces/dog/no.gif[/img]</blockquote><br />\n你呀媽教到你咁 我都覺得好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66afb0b571a8f9f74a76e99cdbd628e269058ce","tid":747830,"uid":7735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T16:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有其中一個醫生話係 比咗啲藥 同特別嘅狗糧 但情況不單冇好轉 呢兩日仲要唔食野 真係好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁有可能係焦慮之類嘅情緒病都唔定"},{"pid":"3a259ad447ec604f98aa9a0eb29c6c67d41cf926","tid":747830,"uid":7735,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T16:56:49.000Z","msg":"佢一係皮膚敏感所以係咁咬自己隻腳 一係就唔開心解悶所以咬自己隻腳 平時有無陪下佢玩同放狗？"},{"pid":"ec41b1f263c93ef54aad76ceaa7a17c7242cb4a6","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T16:57:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪成日得佢自己一個？同埋好少出街行？佢有壓力就會咬自己</blockquote><br />\n唔會呀 屋企因為有細佬 所以全日都有工人 屋企人都朝9晚6 週末係屋企陪佢/帶佢出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好奇一問 點樣知隻狗有壓力 因為我成日覺得隻狗仲嘆過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d86f6d826826f6afa3e3cf0f4ef880d14eebd7e0","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T17:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>心理病。你有無搞到佢壓力大呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？虐待動物？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n虐待動物就唔會上嚟問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>幫佢戴頭罩先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咬到成身傷帶出街隨時被人誤會你虐待動物</blockquote><br />\n其實佢唔止會咬自己啲毛 仲會有腳刮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以唔想要佢戴頭罩搞到佢更加唔開心 因為我地唔知佢究竟咩事 而且又冇改善到情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69a43354f5aa63dcd0cb5f040d6b3b4b36dd73a","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T17:05:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗狗有冇落街嘅習慣 會唔會係惹到一啲皮下嘅寄生蟲 或者皮膚病 肉眼睇唔到但係佢又好痕所以咪不停咬嗰啲位?<br />\n又或者真係情緒有問題 好似有啲狗狗會lam自己隻手嚟解悶同發洩 佢就咬自己啲毛?<br />\n雖然我都有養狗但係真係冇見過咁嘅情況 純粹係推測一下 希望幫到你</blockquote><br />\n醫生攞咗佢啲毛去化驗 結果係冇惹到啲咩皮膚病 但就肯定佢一定係覺得痕 所以先會係咁咬嗰啲位 而且但範圍仲越來越大<br />\n佢有lam呀 但我以爲係佢中意咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11cc6328cd541b95b29e187e13315f1274fe73ef","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T17:08:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有其中一個醫生話係 比咗啲藥 同特別嘅狗糧 但情況不單冇好轉 呢兩日仲要唔食野 真係好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁有可能係焦慮之類嘅情緒病都唔定</blockquote><br />\n巴打有養狗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有冇好醫生介紹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad87b5a3afd18aa13738b6094a2991ea36e94bbb","tid":747830,"uid":124163,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T17:12:05.000Z","msg":"可能係天氣太潮濕都用皮膚敏感架，你google下可以搵到好多有關資料，要長開抽濕機或冷氣先得"},{"pid":"245fcd41a6f9327cfcaa8bb21c1e14452c4e49b8","tid":747830,"uid":95443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T17:17:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40db1b240a5b61f9cba1ddf8ee02752128dc6361","tid":747830,"uid":706,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T17:24:32.000Z","msg":"一係皮膚病 一係心理壓力<br />\n總之一定係有事 睇下有無朋友介紹好醫生比你啦<br />\n<br />\n我睇過太平道npv江醫生唔錯 有耐性同肯用心睇 會詳細解釋講到你明 可以考慮下"},{"pid":"3c90d667de14e5b48a3c6228a81f83724164425e","tid":747830,"uid":82997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec41b1f263c93ef54aad76ceaa7a17c7242cb4a6","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T16:57:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪成日得佢自己一個？同埋好少出街行？佢有壓力就會咬自己</blockquote><br />\n唔會呀 屋企因為有細佬 所以全日都有工人 屋企人都朝9晚6 週末係屋企陪佢/帶佢出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好奇一問 點樣知隻狗有壓力 因為我成日覺得隻狗仲嘆過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T17:28:40.000Z","msg":"咁一個星期先出一次街？定日日都出去？<br />\n有無比玩具佢玩？"},{"pid":"d88d973a8c24dfcbee90a1a7682cabfec669ec68","tid":747830,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T17:30:11.000Z","msg":"工人虐待隻狗？"},{"pid":"731badf48b5a05b47b3204313b299e97dc611c8f","tid":747830,"uid":129824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ec41b1f263c93ef54aad76ceaa7a17c7242cb4a6","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T16:57:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪成日得佢自己一個？同埋好少出街行？佢有壓力就會咬自己</blockquote><br />\n唔會呀 屋企因為有細佬 所以全日都有工人 屋企人都朝9晚6 週末係屋企陪佢/帶佢出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好奇一問 點樣知隻狗有壓力 因為我成日覺得隻狗仲嘆過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T17:30:24.000Z","msg":"最好日日都同佢去下街啊，佢會冇咁悶，行一陣去半個鐘都好"},{"pid":"99d79eed7c544f3abd8ea6ff65f068ca430cf15e","tid":747830,"uid":83557,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T17:35:12.000Z","msg":"未入嚟以為隻狗咬你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9ce709f6db36890de1404783e8be2940896f7c","tid":747830,"uid":8939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T18:04:18.000Z","msg":"會唔會係酵母菌感染？"},{"pid":"83eb5bde813b2c805bf0c880416188db252e4470","tid":747830,"uid":160878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T18:11:43.000Z","msg":"呢種情況要揾牙醫先搞得掂"},{"pid":"6bb6ae17094a18f47fd2f38c9f40e22afa225447","tid":747830,"uid":36025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d86f6d826826f6afa3e3cf0f4ef880d14eebd7e0","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T17:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>心理病。你有無搞到佢壓力大呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？虐待動物？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n虐待動物就唔會上嚟問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>幫佢戴頭罩先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咬到成身傷帶出街隨時被人誤會你虐待動物</blockquote><br />\n其實佢唔止會咬自己啲毛 仲會有腳刮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以唔想要佢戴頭罩搞到佢更加唔開心 因為我地唔知佢究竟咩事 而且又冇改善到情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T18:16:17.000Z","msg":"咬甩晒d毛 vs 帶頭套未必甩咁多<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔帶頭套佢好得番就話姐，但既然你無帶，佢又無好，其實可以試下帶一兩日睇下佢情況點先，起碼阻止左佢咬甩晒d毛(治標)，但係治本個方法都係睇獸醫，聽聞狗狗depress會咬甩晒自己d毛。<br />\n<br />\n我見過有狗主係搵dog train 協助處理狗狗嘅情緒問題！(例如佢長期好不安，可能要係屋企增加啲嘢黎加強安全感) <br />\n<br />\n另外好奇想問下狗狗嘅來曆同埋養左幾耐？"},{"pid":"a57d01a5c4e9d33462494a84f4e28497ceb9ac7c","tid":747830,"uid":36025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T18:25:45.000Z","msg":"另外你隻狗係咪柴犬？(都係純好奇)"},{"pid":"8317ee98a21b1431df718f489bac2d70e78b7d84","tid":747830,"uid":167186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T18:38:34.000Z","msg":"情緒病？"},{"pid":"99e495cb9493b97c2ffb2807c10a8ab9015fae73","tid":747830,"uid":126177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T19:37:02.000Z","msg":"有可能是先囊蟲，遺傳得，正常睇醫生應該醫到架喎。"},{"pid":"3a5e6344a0f3b3c4ad70f443075656d426c4094a","tid":747830,"uid":126177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99e495cb9493b97c2ffb2807c10a8ab9015fae73","tid":747830,"uid":126177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T19:37:02.000Z","msg":"有可能是先囊蟲，遺傳得，正常睇醫生應該醫到架喎。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T19:37:24.000Z","msg":"毛囊蟲"},{"pid":"c27e19938312dbfc074f59ed9829b2c8c7e84a67","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T20:18:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪成日得佢自己一個？同埋好少出街行？佢有壓力就會咬自己</blockquote><br />\n唔會呀 屋企因為有細佬 所以全日都有工人 屋企人都朝9晚6 週末係屋企陪佢/帶佢出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好奇一問 點樣知隻狗有壓力 因為我成日覺得隻狗仲嘆過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>最好日日都同佢去下街啊，佢會冇咁悶，行一陣去半個鐘都好</blockquote><br />\n我地通常兩日一次 因為屋企係村屋 出去走動都好容易 不過最近會密啲 睇下有冇改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0138dad21722926aa3b20c6bb02663f76fd24bdb","tid":747830,"uid":24745,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T20:19:39.000Z","msg":"似皮膚病多過無聊自己咬自己<br />\n我同樓主差唔多平時都係無咩時間陪<br />\n但我屋企隻狗咩事都無 帶佢睇下獸醫啦"},{"pid":"f5f647c1327676d7822a44e9d1e0b4395d4e2944","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T20:19:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係酵母菌感染？</blockquote><br />\n應該唔係 因為醫生攞咗佢啲組織去植毛 返嚟結果咩皮膚病都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e371fe84a55f605ba1a3492dc2730a16ea344ae9","tid":747830,"uid":161364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T20:25:22.000Z","msg":"佢幾歲啊"},{"pid":"e99c17301aa83d63522c0a82dfee5b51c3941999","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T20:26:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>心理病。你有無搞到佢壓力大呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？虐待動物？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n虐待動物就唔會上嚟問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>幫佢戴頭罩先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咬到成身傷帶出街隨時被人誤會你虐待動物</blockquote><br />\n其實佢唔止會咬自己啲毛 仲會有腳刮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以唔想要佢戴頭罩搞到佢更加唔開心 因為我地唔知佢究竟咩事 而且又冇改善到情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>咬甩晒d毛 vs 帶頭套未必甩咁多<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔帶頭套佢好得番就話姐，但既然你無帶，佢又無好，其實可以試下帶一兩日睇下佢情況點先，起碼阻止左佢咬甩晒d毛(治標)，但係治本個方法都係睇獸醫，聽聞狗狗depress會咬甩晒自己d毛。<br />\n<br />\n我見過有狗主係搵dog train 協助處理狗狗嘅情緒問題！(例如佢長期好不安，可能要係屋企增加啲嘢黎加強安全感) <br />\n<br />\n另外好奇想問下狗狗嘅來曆同埋養左幾耐？</blockquote><br />\n 好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拎養返嚟㗎 10個月 養咗8個月啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359c70ba6fc613608a9ae86903e014fd90de4d26","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T20:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外你隻狗係咪柴犬？(都係純好奇)</blockquote><br />\n係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多謝巴打比咁多建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae09b35efa6f169579376b89cf2e061ea5f3f3d","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T20:28:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>另外你隻狗係咪柴犬？(都係純好奇)</blockquote><br />\n係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多謝巴打比咁多建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSorry 係絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f83643b2436d08846adf998afa840d8dbc9f5e7","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T20:30:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>情緒病？</blockquote><br />\n有其中一個醫生話係 但我哋仲未搵出點解佢會有<br />\n另一個醫生就話係敏感<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b130c1b77372ce656d2524e1140da4429d979cb","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T20:34:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有可能是先囊蟲，遺傳得，正常睇醫生應該醫到架喎。</blockquote><br />\n佢啲皮膚冇傷口 只係咬甩自己啲毛<br />\n同埋醫生check 過佢冇皮膚病呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e62b403b1518aa87c5772fbc1098258d8fc9ea6e","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T20:35:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似皮膚病多過無聊自己咬自己<br />\n我同樓主差唔多平時都係無咩時間陪<br />\n但我屋企隻狗咩事都無 帶佢睇下獸醫啦</blockquote><br />\n帶咗佢睇兩個獸醫都冇改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc8c335f6011db005b6cdc09b56b7db971a5b51","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T20:35:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢幾歲啊</blockquote><br />\n10個月大啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58161dc6586265240d9867215fc1269e3d414bcd","tid":747830,"uid":162689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7b130c1b77372ce656d2524e1140da4429d979cb","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T20:34:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有可能是先囊蟲，遺傳得，正常睇醫生應該醫到架喎。</blockquote><br />\n佢啲皮膚冇傷口 只係咬甩自己啲毛<br />\n同埋醫生check 過佢冇皮膚病呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T21:18:59.000Z","msg":"首先要rule out係唔係皮膚病 <br />\n皮膚過敏嗰D皮膚會有傷口 （例如肚仔，鐘意舔手腳）<br />\n寄生蟲 （例如毛囊蝎）會好癢，如果巴打有worming tablet嘅話，應該唔洗咁擔心<br />\n至於癬嗰D，如果醫生有send去lab嘅話會知結果<br />\n<br />\n其次就係行為所引至，樓主隻狗睇落似情緒病多D<br />\n一般獸醫好難揾到係咩引至咁，建議睇behavioural specialist<br />\n如果唔係可以試下含有pheromones嘅產品 （例如adaptil）依D都係會令到狗狗放鬆D，但唔一定work"},{"pid":"00e97f05f585fee6a1e9ca0baf60ff330f8f6ef2","tid":747830,"uid":147242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T21:57:02.000Z","msg":"狗都會有精神病<br />\n不過要察覺好難"},{"pid":"0230299b3154d3e292334f7bdae7c78cc7ee8e90","tid":747830,"uid":5128,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T23:57:45.000Z","msg":"情緒病<br />\n我隻狗以前都有<br />\n後尾陪佢多d 同佢玩多d 就解決哂"},{"pid":"3485f3e89cbab69b770a7421349ec31cdd34b8c1","tid":747830,"uid":156623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T00:13:28.000Z","msg":"係心理壓力導致 之前睇動物節目都有隻狗想咬甩自己條尾自殘 <br />\n希望樓主花多啲時間陪佢啦"},{"pid":"8c9f80aec2d44922df30f14ee0c2b39488484d47","tid":747830,"uid":14766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T00:25:55.000Z","msg":"如果係柴 真係好容易會有皮膚病"},{"pid":"f464e8c07e212814fe41f9e68e46d16d4b62d1aa","tid":747830,"uid":40812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:06:33.000Z","msg":"一係皮膚病<br />\n一係心理問題<br />\n<br />\n建議睇咗醫生rule out咗皮膚病先"},{"pid":"b42f4bb7ef6ee687352bd7f78825b505fb453e8d","tid":747830,"uid":40812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f464e8c07e212814fe41f9e68e46d16d4b62d1aa","tid":747830,"uid":40812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:06:33.000Z","msg":"一係皮膚病<br />\n一係心理問題<br />\n<br />\n建議睇咗醫生rule out咗皮膚病先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:07:50.000Z","msg":"原來上面有人講晒，打擾了。"},{"pid":"5ccebda9071eddc7fb7db83b032999c846f4d3cf","tid":747830,"uid":112950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:38:37.000Z","msg":"因為怕佢唔開心所以唔幫佢帶頭套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你以為自己為佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔識養寵物真係唔好養"},{"pid":"fa8c190559c992b67b68134cef80a551c8d1ad1c","tid":747830,"uid":194123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:46:54.000Z","msg":"佢食咩牌子狗糧？咩肉既成份？"},{"pid":"c1e4f4ec1eb6a952751242e25c75bb147ecfcf23","tid":747830,"uid":36025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"359c70ba6fc613608a9ae86903e014fd90de4d26","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T20:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外你隻狗係咪柴犬？(都係純好奇)</blockquote><br />\n係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多謝巴打比咁多建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T01:58:54.000Z","msg":"我都係養柴，少啲見柴犬有皮膚問題，fb 有兩個柴犬group 啲人好有經驗，你可以post上去問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10914027957f8406a4c4c089b819d197c227c26a","tid":747830,"uid":100817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T02:17:25.000Z","msg":"兩日出一次街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地個個有自己既社交圈子 又可以周圍去<br />\n但係佢既世界得你屋企咁大<br />\n俾著我都有精神病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得起碼一日一次 玩到隻狗攰先ok"},{"pid":"2399d58bf8c81f2572f61c9b65c9710678988a76","tid":747830,"uid":129374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T02:33:22.000Z","msg":"你隻狗唔似係皮膚病, 似係情緒問題. 佢係好撚無聊先會咬自己.<br />\n其實柴犬算戶外犬種, 你兩日先出一次街. 不如送比人咪撚養佢.<br />\n我隻狗狗算中小型犬都一日出三次街,星期六日重會帶佢出去遠行.<br />\n其他附近嘅狗友最少都每日帶佢出去散步一次啦."},{"pid":"b6b403bbac7a570944a456d8f6fd5eadef105f94","tid":747830,"uid":40273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43b70142672c7409c7739628523a9dbc3fdea2a4","tid":747830,"uid":139185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T16:32:41.000Z","msg":"就嚟冇曬啲毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n有冇人知咩事 已經睇過幾次醫生 個個都唔同講法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/002812_f87fc5e62deef5798f745eb48710f620.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F002812_f87fc5e62deef5798f745eb48710f620.jpg&h=5fc90937&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/002817_61962e53a2849da8850ac4784891ea88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F002817_61962e53a2849da8850ac4784891ea88.jpg&h=db8e339b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:41:46.000Z","msg":"我隻狗以前都係咁，冇人喺屋企就咬到大脾位d毛甩晒，有人喺屋企佢就唔咬，冇辦法架喇，唯有屋企有人睇住佢啦"},{"pid":"60f07d907d69b380bfb1950b1f9ba6b599f7f6b0","tid":747830,"uid":22087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:48:58.000Z","msg":"皮膚病甩毛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e81818dcf7a5d6ec73c724186ce9020e6d1c3e","tid":747830,"uid":123790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:53:01.000Z","msg":"我隻哥姬之前都試過, 係因為痕, 睇完醫生之後又係無皮膚病以為無事, 過一排又咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後而加只要唔係睇住佢就幫佢帶個罩, 咁佢就咬唔到自己"},{"pid":"975f8837bfffe65e19d6e422a5e78eabcb8656c8","tid":747830,"uid":123790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6b4